title: New Creator: Wuki
body:
Name: Wuki

Socials -
https://twitter.com/Wuki
https://solo.to/wuki

Info - Wuki is a Grammy nominated producer, remixer, and DJ that specializes in extremely unique and creative mash ups. Wuki has a very dedicated fan base that is very engaged across all of his platforms. Wuki is very excited about the direction of crypto and believes that his community will really benefit from the various types of engagement that can be accessed through his coin.    

Use Cases -
Coin distribution - Social media push / Discord /  Twitch 
Holding - Access to exclusive Discord roles and channels, community events, access to exclusive mash ups and remixes
Transacting - Twitch song requests, collaborations, merch, 1 on 1 work

Grant - $1000

A 'yes' approves Wuki and a $1000 treasury grant
A 'no' denies this prop.
